## Release Process Instructions
### Version Management
1. Update version number in [pyproject.toml](mdc:pyproject.toml):
   - Ask the user about the version: new major, minor, patch
   - Follow semantic versioning (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)
   - Ensure version number matches planned release
2. Update [CHANGELOG.md](mdc:CHANGELOG.md):
   - Add section for new version
   - Document all significant changes
   - Include any breaking changes
   - Add contributor acknowledgments

### Release Commits
1. Create release commit:
   ```powershell
   git add pyproject.toml CHANGELOG.md
   git commit -m "vX.X.X"
   ```

### Release Tagging
1. Create and push git tag:
    ```powershell
    git tag -a vX.X.X -m "vX.X.X"
    ```

Note: Replace X.X.X with the actual version number throughout these steps. 


